[Floated in Dungeon Areas ( Press and Hold Circle+L1) Use Left Analog Sticks to Move Backward or Forward]
author=12345
description=In new game+ (playing for the second time), Seraphic Gate unlocked at the beginning of the game. Enter the Seraphic Gate, don't talk to a woman(Dirna), so activated the floated code (press and hold Circle+L1), keep levitating until reach the top of the screen. And then press and hold forward (use left analog sticks), still hold L1, then press the Circle button repeatedly until through the woman, release the floated button and return to the ground. Now can explore the Seraphic Gate and unlock the cool character.
But the character like Valkyrie,Freya,Lenneth,Silmeria and Hrist could not be use in battles (the game will crash) 
patch=1,EE,E004DBFF,extended,001CA1DC
patch=1,EE,6048E1E8,extended,00000100
patch=1,EE,00010000,extended,000002BC
patch=1,EE,6048E1E8,extended,C1061000
patch=1,EE,00020000,extended,000002C4

